title: A New STEALTH Price Hike from GW for Warcry (and maybe Kill Team?)
description:
We're getting some freedom of choice in this "season" of Warcry - but at what cost? 30% more - about $57 actually. And it'll probably happen to Kill Team, too. 

Vince Venturella and I made a 'zine! Check out SNARL at http://www.snarlingbadger.com/snarl
